=head1 INSTALLATION

These are the installation instructions for App::drophandler.

The module releases are hosted on CPAN. The module
can be installed:

=over

=item latest release from CPAN

  cpan App::drophandler

or

  cpanm App::drophandler

=item directly, as the latest development files

 cpanm git://github.com/Corion/app-drophandler.git

=item manually cloninig the repository:

 git clone git://github.com/Corion/app-drophandler.git
 cd App_drophandler
 perl Makefile.PL
 make
 make test
 make install

=back

